1. To run the adapter for power flow data conversion to ODM, 
   please add "loadflow" in the first row of the file the is going 
   to be converted. please see the test data: testdata--bpa--014bpa.DAT.
   
   
2.To run the adapter for power flow and transient data conversion to ODM, 
   Please copy the transient data, and paste it to the end of power flow data sheet,
   right following the (END) sign of the power flow data sheet.    
   Then,please add "transient" in the first row of the file the is going 
   to be converted.
   
3. The transient data conversion part has not been fully tested, and it
   needs to be developed and tested more in future.
